name: Changing Tire
description: techniques to reduce the file size of your WEBP, JPEG and PNG files. By selectively decreasing the number of colors in the image, fewer bytes are required to store the data. The effect is nearly invisible but it makes a very large difference in file size!Why should I use TinyPNG? PNG is useful because it’s the only widely supported format that can store partially transparent images.
